    <div class="well" id="current-twitter-hack-debate" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.current.com/debate">Current + Twitter = Hack the Debate</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>A little project that&#8217;s been going on here at Current Towers - During the presidential debates, we&#8217;ll be diving into Twitter and putting the *real* debate up on national TV in real(ish) time.  (And who&#8217;s that handsome avatar halfway through the promo…?)</p>

