<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/jun/03/">&#x27a0;</a> June 3, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="video-speech-matching-theywork" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.theyworkforyou.com/video/">Video speech matching (TheyWorkForYou.com)</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>TheyWorkForYou has a crowdsourcing project matching the Hansard transcripts of parliamentary debates to BBC video.  It&#8217;s pretty easy work if you keep going through one debate (and you get to watch a little bit of politics in action).  Fancy taking a half hour to help them out?</p>

