<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/mar/03/">&#x27a0;</a> March 3, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="hour-and-half-barack-obama" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://blog.pmarca.com/2008/03/an-hour-and-a-h.html">An hour and a half with Barack Obama</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;What&#8217;s the picture that emerges from these four impressions?</p>

<p>Smart, normal, curious, not radical, and post-Boomer.</p>

<p>If you were asking me to write a capsule description of what I would look for in the next President of the United States, that would be it.&#8221;</p>

